#

Classic Cheeseburger with Sweet Potato Fries

$15.99
800 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

Nut-freeDairy-inclusive

Tags:

PopularComfort FoodQuick

Description

A juicy cheeseburger topped with melted cheese and served with crispy sweet potato fries.

Ingredients

  • Ground beef: 1 lb
  • Cheddar cheese: 4 slices
  • Burger buns: 4
  • Sweet potatoes: 2 large
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Lettuce: 4 leaves
  • Tomato: 1, sliced
  • Pickles: to taste
